{"tid":1567382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[終極維穩] 中国開始大力科水俾維穩社團跟撚住我哋做野","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:19:59.000Z","uid":112814,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21a11ddab744e96f851af92a1b8c63f10ddd6ba1","tid":1567382,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"維穩社團開始做野 行動方針就係「我地做咩佢哋就做咩」既小學雞式行動<br />\n我哋唱歌 佢哋跟住唱<br />\n我哋上獅子山 佢哋跟住上 <br />\n目的就係挑釁 以身為餌幫共狗吸引火力<br />\n老實講 依班小醜其實唔使理 因為佢哋捱唔到一個禮拜 <br />\n我哋只需要堅持做番自己野 佢哋除左挑釁性之外對我哋Or國際傳媒其實都係零影響力<br />\n點解要出到維穩社團呀 就係共狗招數已經出盡 <br />\n黑警831之後已經全面含撚 正式成為老鼠 淨係應付太子站單野已經焦頭爛額 錯漏百出<br />\n咁就唯有靠社團頂住先 但係社團呢 就要科水 成千蚊個人頭 可想而知根本唔會捱到幾耐 <br />\n都變相話俾我哋聽佢哋係好驚俾我哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">10月1送大禮 </span></span></strong><br />\n大家唔使驚我保證班社團係捱唔到一個禮拜"},{"pid":"2211bee34cf4238ec823934224d0632c9ce44896","tid":1567382,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:16:23.000Z","msg":"千其唔好去幫人添人頭<br />\n反cup雖然好好睇<br />\n但班撚屌無恥到屈人頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65cf4690c08d8aaa9606617d3277c7f38aa3871","tid":1567382,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:16:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05d1880f1308747c9ca15f5fa6b88d9134cb253c","tid":1567382,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fcbe6401e5d67e523356acc4744268d0cf40b1f","tid":1567382,"uid":112